- **No Hardcoded Secrets**: Ensure credentials, tokens, or private URLs are loaded from environment variables (see [.env.example](file://./.env.example)). Never commit active `.env` files.
- **Code Documentation**: Maintain documentation integrity. Keep existing comments and docstrings intact.
